Known as the Winter Warlock, Aseroth is the ruler of the 566th Layer of the+Abyss, called Soulfreeze.Â  He is the lord of ice and cold.
Soulfreeze has a two-way portal to the Paraelemental+Plane+of+Ice. The key is a mortal soul, which is destroyed in the process.
